---
description: Require moving issues to In Progress before starting work
alwaysApply: true
---

## Issue Workflow

- If the user asks you to work on a tracked issue and you are about to begin substantive work, first move that issue to `In Progress`.
- Do this before research, implementation, testing, or review work begins.
- If the issue is not identified clearly enough to update its status, ask for the issue ID or link before starting work.
